headline.main: ROOSEVELT SEES MUSSOLINI'S ENVOY; Talk at Ambassador's Request --No Plan to Warn Americans in Italy, Welles Says

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, May 2--President Roosevelt emerged definitely today as a direct participant in the exchanges that are taking place between Italy and the United States when he conferred with Prince Ascanio Colonna, the Italian Ambassador.
